<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="141380000t" end="151900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">原来如此</p>
<p begin="152140000t" end="166090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">这可是重症呢</p>
<p begin="170860000t" end="206230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">真亏你能活着撑到现在呢</p>
<p begin="206480000t" end="224050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">你…你是谁</p>
<p begin="346750000t" end="377270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">连发散累积的玛那的方式都不知道</p>
<p begin="385080000t" end="411600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">我真是对你的<br />理解力之低感到悲哀啊…</p>
<p begin="687660000t" end="698100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">怎么样</p>
<p begin="702630000t" end="722450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">稍微轻松一点了吧</p>
<p begin="726360000t" end="748470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">你…你做了什么</p>
<p begin="748710000t" end="767750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">女性竟然…做这种事…</p>
<p begin="776350000t" end="801840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">我只是直接把玛那给吸出来而已啊</p>
<p begin="813630000t" end="823660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">玛那?</p>
<p begin="823900000t" end="847610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">你这并不是疾病</p>
<p begin="852460000t" end="867910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">只是被称为发魔期的现象罢了</p>
<p begin="873340000t" end="891340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">发魔…期</p>
<p begin="896190000t" end="914710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">确实是非常稀少的案例</p>
<p begin="919550000t" end="958750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">所以至今为止应该没有任何人<br />能够理解你吧</p>
<p begin="971800000t" end="1005400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">但是我能够理解你的痛苦</p>
<p begin="1005640000t" end="1034540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">因为我也有过一样的经验</p>
<p begin="1174380000t" end="1198150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">你…你到底是…</p>
<p begin="1204320000t" end="1220730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">我是魔女</p>
<p begin="1230650000t" end="1251150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">是偶尔也会做好事的</p>
<p begin="1251390000t" end="1266500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">邪恶魔女喔</p>
<p begin="1277900000t" end="1288390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">你呢</p>
<p begin="1353280000t" end="1368750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">怎么样呢, 贝蒂</p>
<p begin="1369000000t" end="1388260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">我和老师恋情的开端</p>
<p begin="1388500000t" end="1400540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">什么怎么样的</p>
<p begin="1400790000t" end="1432460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">我可是一分一毫都没问过你啊</p>
<p begin="1432700000t" end="1448850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">还有恋情的开端什么的</p>
<p begin="1449090000t" end="1469530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">对母亲大人来说也太随便了吧</p>
<p begin="1469770000t" end="1479370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">也是呢</p>
<p begin="1479610000t" end="1492470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">不过是开端而已</p>
<p begin="1492710000t" end="1534760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">但是我还记得那时<br />老师说过的每一句话</p>
<p begin="1535000000t" end="1563350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">对母亲大人而言可是困扰而已</p>
<p begin="1563590000t" end="1585310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">当然对贝蒂来说也是</p>
<p begin="1589690000t" end="1602460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">碧翠丝大人</p>
<p begin="1602700000t" end="1621250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">不需要说成这样吧</p>
<p begin="1626560000t" end="1649930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">而且罗兹瓦尔大人的心情</p>
<p begin="1650170000t" end="1666480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">我也能够理解</p>
<p begin="1666720000t" end="1684990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">因为我也是被艾姬多娜大人</p>
<p begin="1685240000t" end="1699790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">给拯救的其中一人啊</p>
<p begin="1726200000t" end="1752890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">琉兹君也必须好好答谢老师才行呢</p>
<p begin="1756400000t" end="1764910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">是的</p>
<p begin="1768980000t" end="1799290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">如果那天我没和老师相遇的话</p>
<p begin="1802800000t" end="1826640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">现在应该也还在一个人独自痛苦着吧</p>
<p begin="1833980000t" end="1858330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">或者是和世界道别</p>
<p begin="1858570000t" end="1879610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">早早就离开了也说不定</p>
<p begin="1884880000t" end="1897280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">没有变成那样</p>
<p begin="1897600000t" end="1918950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">顺利让父母和兄弟刮目相看</p>
<p begin="1919190000t" end="1936880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">并成功夺回梅札斯家的实权</p>
<p begin="1942890000t" end="1961500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">也全部都是老师的功劳</p>
<p begin="1973300000t" end="1992510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">真是个厚颜无耻的男人</p>
<p begin="1992750000t" end="2006630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">什么都说成感谢强加在别人身上</p>
<p begin="2006880000t" end="2021990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">真不是个大男人该做的事</p>
<p begin="2022230000t" end="2044640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">不过碧翠丝大人也常说</p>
<p begin="2044880000t" end="2076090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">"要好好感谢才行"耶</p>
<p begin="2076330000t" end="2110150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">你到底是贝蒂还是罗兹瓦尔的伙伴啊</p>
<p begin="2138430000t" end="2178520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">我不喜欢你这家伙<br />这种奇怪的温暖眼神</p>
<p begin="2182270000t" end="2194390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">你有什么意见的话</p>
<p begin="2194630000t" end="2206240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">就放马过来啊</p>
<p begin="2206480000t" end="2226120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">我爱你喔</p>
<p begin="2226360000t" end="2251390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">少说那些让人恶心的话了</p>
<p begin="2268500000t" end="2278440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">老师</p>
<p begin="2282810000t" end="2300340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">你们3个都在这里啊</p>
<p begin="2313150000t" end="2332920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">有好好相处没有吵架吗</p>
<p begin="2333160000t" end="2342760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">当然了</p>
<p begin="2343000000t" end="2354570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">当然的吧</p>
<p begin="2385350000t" end="2398130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">真是的</p>
<p begin="2398370000t" end="2430660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">看来还是一群需要费心的孩子们呢</p>
<p begin="2480810000t" end="2504070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">你听说了这样的事情啊</p>
<p begin="2508690000t" end="2517310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">是的</p>
<p begin="2517550000t" end="2535840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">这是希玛在墓所看见的</p>
<p begin="2536080000t" end="2554660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">琉兹·梅耶尔的记忆</p>
<p begin="2554900000t" end="2569940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">原来如此</p>
<p begin="2570170000t" end="2612570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">那么你也知道"那一天"的事情了吧</p>
<p begin="2623510000t" end="2661240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">这个圣域诞生的, 那一天</p>
<p begin="2679680000t" end="2717340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">罗兹瓦尔真是个让人生气的家伙</p>
<p begin="2717580000t" end="2737800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">无论如何都不能轻易原谅他</p>
<p begin="2738040000t" end="2749170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">话说回来本来就是因为</p>
<p begin="2749410000t" end="2777360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">碧翠丝大人对我恶作剧</p>
<p begin="2777600000t" end="2788590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">才会变成要和罗兹瓦尔大人</p>
<p begin="2788830000t" end="2811120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">敌对的局面不是吗</p>
<p begin="2811360000t" end="2841070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">不…不要说什么恶作剧啦</p>
<p begin="2841380000t" end="2851240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">那个是更那个…</p>
<p begin="2851480000t" end="2867610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">高尚的东西啦</p>
<p begin="2867850000t" end="2897020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">不管开了几扇门都是同一个房间</p>
<p begin="2897260000t" end="2929630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">对我来说可是非常恐怖的回忆呢</p>
<p begin="2936900000t" end="2963610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">只是一点阴魔法的应用啦</p>
<p begin="2963850000t" end="2988860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">也不必用那种责备的眼神看我…</p>
<p begin="2993480000t" end="3021650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">原来如此, 这样的话用反魔法</p>
<p begin="3021890000t" end="3049670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">做出类似的方式反击的我</p>
<p begin="3049910000t" end="3075620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">也难怪你没露出责备的眼神了</p>
<p begin="3091870000t" end="3113110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">表情不错呢, 碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="3118890000t" end="3135710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">继老师之后我第二喜欢的</p>
<p begin="3136120000t" end="3158330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">就是你的那个表情了喔</p>
<p begin="3158570000t" end="3177740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">你在说什么啦</p>
<p begin="3177980000t" end="3189000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">你这家伙只不过是好运</p>
<p begin="3189240000t" end="3208370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">被赋予一点才能和家世</p>
<p begin="3208620000t" end="3237150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">还得到世界上最好的老师而已</p>
<p begin="3237390000t" end="3255730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">少在那边嚣张了</p>
<p begin="3255970000t" end="3266670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">碧翠丝大人</p>
<p begin="3266910000t" end="3290240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">您这是在夸他吧…</p>
<p begin="3290490000t" end="3300500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">琉兹君</p>
<p begin="3300740000t" end="3319420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">如果你又被碧翠丝为难的话</p>
<p begin="3319660000t" end="3335180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">随时和我说也无妨</p>
<p begin="3335420000t" end="3350200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">我会马上惩罚她</p>
<p begin="3350440000t" end="3368400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">打她小屁屁的</p>
<p begin="3378010000t" end="3412390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">这孩子根本完全没有<br />依靠过你任何事好吗</p>
<p begin="3412630000t" end="3427880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">对吧, 你说啊</p>
<p begin="3434520000t" end="3449550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">谢谢您</p>
<p begin="3449790000t" end="3464550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">那么如果有遇到的时候</p>
<p begin="3464790000t" end="3480770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">我会再和您报告的</p>
<p begin="3484680000t" end="3504510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">这算什么啦</p>
<p begin="3527010000t" end="3547480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">抱歉打扰你读书了</p>
<p begin="3547720000t" end="3571310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">我这就代替碧翠丝和你道个歉</p>
<p begin="3571550000t" end="3597560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">不, 您不需要这样的</p>
<p begin="3597800000t" end="3632960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">而且, 这应该还不能称为读书…</p>
<p begin="3651010000t" end="3674550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">读书是好的</p>
<p begin="3674790000t" end="3704960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">会让人生变得丰富</p>
<p begin="3705200000t" end="3712360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">正是如此</p>
<p begin="3712600000t" end="3744460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">碧翠丝还真会把老师教的东西现学现卖呢</p>
<p begin="3765770000t" end="3790070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">对了, 既然这样碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="3790400000t" end="3820610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">你要不要来当琉兹君的老师呢</p>
<p begin="3820850000t" end="3842220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">贝蒂来教…这孩子…</p>
<p begin="3842460000t" end="3860810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">这…这种事…</p>
<p begin="3861050000t" end="3896510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">怎么能给忙碌的碧翠丝大人添麻烦</p>
<p begin="3896750000t" end="3927090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">当…当一下也不是不行</p>
<p begin="3931460000t" end="3954970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">小事一桩而已啦</p>
<p begin="3974150000t" end="3985700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">怎么了</p>
<p begin="3985940000t" end="4009140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">不喜欢的话也不勉强</p>
<p begin="4009380000t" end="4028260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">贝蒂也不是那么有兴趣…</p>
<p begin="4028500000t" end="4035630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">不</p>
<p begin="4035870000t" end="4061930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">能被碧翠丝大人教导的话</p>
<p begin="4062170000t" end="4081770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">那就太开心了</p>
<p begin="4093340000t" end="4111500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">你…你都说到这样</p>
<p begin="4111740000t" end="4126540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">那就没办法了</p>
<p begin="4126780000t" end="4151580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">你真是个幸运的孩子呢</p>
<p begin="4196040000t" end="4209480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">碧翠丝大人</p>
<p begin="4214800000t" end="4233400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">母亲大人在呼唤我</p>
<p begin="4266370000t" end="4277170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">罗兹瓦尔</p>
<p begin="4277410000t" end="4299050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">母亲大人也叫你一起过去</p>
<p begin="4299290000t" end="4314200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">看来是有紧急的事</p>
<p begin="4318490000t" end="4328750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">我知道了</p>
<p begin="4332110000t" end="4341960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">看来是…</p>
<p begin="4350870000t" end="4361610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">那家伙来了</p>
<p begin="4447230000t" end="4459980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">确认过了</p>
<p begin="4465840000t" end="4478980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">果然是那个男人</p>
<p begin="4490390000t" end="4499050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">是吗</p>
