<p begin="9034940000t" end="9060980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">你们就尽管用劳动来回报吧</p>
<p begin="9112350000t" end="9122210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">总觉得</p>
<p begin="9122540000t" end="9148760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">你好像用很讨人厌的表情在笑</p>
<p begin="9219690000t" end="9238060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">真的很抱歉</p>
<p begin="9238300000t" end="9259440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">有一些脏东西跑到眼睛里了</p>
<p begin="9273970000t" end="9283070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">果然</p>
<p begin="9283320000t" end="9309040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">你还是在这里好好待着吧</p>
<p begin="9309280000t" end="9337620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">贝蒂去帮母亲大人助阵</p>
<p begin="9337860000t" end="9379580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">也必须去帮帮快死掉的罗兹瓦尔才行</p>
<p begin="9379820000t" end="9401640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">然后, 等明天之后再来</p>
<p begin="9432270000t" end="9444490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">碧翠丝大人</p>
<p begin="9453790000t" end="9478740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">感谢您这么长时间的照顾</p>
<p begin="9482720000t" end="9489570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">咦</p>
<p begin="9497220000t" end="9517090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">我在此向您道别</p>
<p begin="9522790000t" end="9546440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">道别是什么意思</p>
<p begin="9550180000t" end="9596900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">为了让森林布满结界<br />我们在这个设施做了准备</p>
<p begin="9597140000t" end="9611950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">以我为内核</p>
<p begin="9612190000t" end="9632810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">花时间慢慢地完成结界</p>
<p begin="9633060000t" end="9642820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">但是</p>
<p begin="9643060000t" end="9668840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">看来时间似乎是不太够了</p>
<p begin="9669080000t" end="9692410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">为了结界所安排的时间…</p>
<p begin="9692660000t" end="9720510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">要, 要是被那个男人妨碍的话…</p>
<p begin="9720760000t" end="9738860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">光是战斗的话赢不了</p>
<p begin="9739100000t" end="9756370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">也是因为这样才需要"圣域"</p>
<p begin="9761530000t" end="9790230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">罗兹瓦尔大人会牺牲这么多</p>
<p begin="9790470000t" end="9802680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">也是因为知道如果不这么做的话</p>
<p begin="9802920000t" end="9828400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">是救不了艾姬多娜大人的</p>
<p begin="9840120000t" end="9854630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">只要能制作出结界</p>
<p begin="9854870000t" end="9869940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">就能够保护这里</p>
<p begin="9878300000t" end="9907240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">我就是为此而献身的</p>
<p begin="9912010000t" end="9937280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">别开玩笑了</p>
<p begin="9937520000t" end="9954470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">即使你献出自己的肉体</p>
<p begin="9954710000t" end="9989650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">不懂魔法的你又能做些什么</p>
<p begin="9989890000t" end="10000650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">你又…</p>
<p begin="10045730000t" end="10071350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">以这个魔法水晶为触媒</p>
<p begin="10071590000t" end="10100990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">将你的欧德作为内核制作结界…?</p>
<p begin="10108640000t" end="10116540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">是的</p>
<p begin="10121540000t" end="10144680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">这是艾姬多娜大人所想出来的</p>
<p begin="10155700000t" end="10163480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">等等</p>
<p begin="10163720000t" end="10175050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">这样不对</p>
<p begin="10175290000t" end="10211320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">贝蒂现在马上去和母亲大人重新谈谈</p>
<p begin="10211560000t" end="10231640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">母亲大人很疼贝蒂</p>
<p begin="10231890000t" end="10240270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">一定会听的</p>
<p begin="10240500000t" end="10256520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">已经没有时间了</p>
<p begin="10256750000t" end="10286760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">现在需要马上做决定</p>
<p begin="10287010000t" end="10294830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">如果是这样</p>
<p begin="10295070000t" end="10324930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">去帮母亲大人助阵就是贝蒂的决定</p>
<p begin="10329480000t" end="10346500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">只要母亲大人和贝蒂一起的话</p>
<p begin="10346750000t" end="10364060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">那种家伙一下子就能干掉了</p>
<p begin="10390890000t" end="10431560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">用贝蒂的"机遇门"让大家<br />从这里逃走就好了</p>
<p begin="10450470000t" end="10458100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">对吧</p>
<p begin="10458350000t" end="10474310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">就这样做吧</p>
<p begin="10474550000t" end="10500760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">虽然人太多的话贝蒂也会很辛苦</p>
<p begin="10501000000t" end="10520080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">这点程度我就撑一下吧</p>
<p begin="10520320000t" end="10541050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">找机会把罗兹瓦尔捡走</p>
<p begin="10541290000t" end="10559540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">然后把母亲大人给带出来</p>
<p begin="10559930000t" end="10575010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">你看, 这样就…</p>
<p begin="10614770000t" end="10630680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">像这样落荒而逃</p>
<p begin="10630930000t" end="10659240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">然后又要过着不知道<br />什么时候会被追上的日子吗</p>
<p begin="10667520000t" end="10693780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">这是多亏了艾姬多娜大人<br />和罗兹瓦尔大人</p>
<p begin="10694020000t" end="10717070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">才好不容易得到的安宁之地</p>
<p begin="10722620000t" end="10759500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">舍弃这里, 再重新建构一个圣域</p>
<p begin="10759740000t" end="10777130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">又要花上多长的时间呢</p>
<p begin="10788150000t" end="10805590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">我已经</p>
<p begin="10805830000t" end="10826880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">得到了很多温暖的时刻</p>
<p begin="10839130000t" end="10859730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">我很喜欢这个地方</p>
<p begin="10865280000t" end="10895000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">真心觉得能够生活在这里真是太好了</p>
<p begin="10901250000t" end="10933530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">也因为最喜欢在这里生活的人们的笑容</p>
<p begin="10945400000t" end="10967420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">所以, 我不想失去它</p>
<p begin="10985230000t" end="11016830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">不管你认为这个地方怎么样</p>
<p begin="11017070000t" end="11046180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">这里都不是真的为了你们而设的场所</p>
<p begin="11046420000t" end="11053820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">是的</p>
<p begin="11058750000t" end="11070580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">我知道</p>
<p begin="11082850000t" end="11096750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">既然这样</p>
<p begin="11096990000t" end="11111970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">既然你都知道</p>
<p begin="11112210000t" end="11124100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">那为什么还要…</p>
<p begin="11141370000t" end="11152470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">没关系</p>
<p begin="11152710000t" end="11176530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">最初的时候, 可能真的是那样</p>
<p begin="11186210000t" end="11194870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">但是</p>
<p begin="11207140000t" end="11235110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">我们在这里度过的时间</p>
<p begin="11240290000t" end="11262790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">已经全都和最初不一样了</p>
<p begin="11276690000t" end="11294840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">我在这里生活</p>
<p begin="11295080000t" end="11317950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">以及我能够和碧翠丝大人交谈</p>
<p begin="11322100000t" end="11331130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">这些</p>
<p begin="11331370000t" end="11358780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">都是由我依自己的意识而做的选择</p>
<p begin="11371600000t" end="11401920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">我并非失去了全部</p>
<p begin="11408640000t" end="11441010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">而是怀抱着所有我获得的东西</p>
<p begin="11454680000t" end="11475510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">能在这里生活我很幸福</p>
<p begin="11480520000t" end="11493110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">所以</p>
<p begin="11493350000t" end="11514070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">我会为了自己想守护的<br />这些珍贵的时刻</p>
<p begin="11514310000t" end="11525020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">而去做的</p>
<p begin="11534310000t" end="11555230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">我想对碧翠丝大人无数次</p>
<p begin="11555470000t" end="11583590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">即使现在也不断帮助我的恩情</p>
<p begin="11588130000t" end="11606640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">表达感谢</p>
<p begin="11690070000t" end="11703450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">碧翠丝大人</p>
<p begin="11731420000t" end="11768360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">请注意不要吃太多甜食喔</p>
<p begin="11892800000t" end="11951400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">教, 教你读书的约定还…</p>
<p begin="12083490000t" end="12095330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">谢谢你</p>
<p begin="12238990000t" end="12249110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">再见了</p>
<p begin="12258000000t" end="12267570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">贝蒂</p>
<p begin="12321660000t" end="12356890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">这些就是我听到的全部了</p>
<p begin="12371820000t" end="12381850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">然后呢</p>
<p begin="12387630000t" end="12409580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">就算这件事是真的</p>
<p begin="12409820000t" end="12430470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">你又打算如何?</p>
<p begin="12437420000t" end="12448720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">我再说一次</p>
<p begin="12448960000t" end="12459010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">投降吧</p>
<p begin="12463460000t" end="12480840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">风向改变了</p>
<p begin="12481080000t" end="12502930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">阻止正在前往宅邸的那些人吧</p>
<p begin="12503170000t" end="12524300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">这样的话我们应该就能达成协议</p>
<p begin="12545480000t" end="12565850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">我拒绝喔, 昴君</p>
<p begin="12572720000t" end="12594070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">我的四百年可没有轻率到</p>
<p begin="12594310000t" end="12618180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">能够被这种程度的变化所动摇</p>
<p begin="12625840000t" end="12647430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">从外面带来新的援兵</p>
<p begin="12647740000t" end="12662220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">并将加菲尔除去以后</p>
<p begin="12662470000t" end="12683390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">就以为自己能占尽优势的话</p>
<p begin="12683640000t" end="12696120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">那就大错特错了</p>
<p begin="12696360000t" end="12705980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">你说什么</p>
<p begin="12706220000t" end="12720130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">我说错了吗</p>
<p begin="12725130000t" end="12758950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">那么一心作势要咬死外人的你</p>
<p begin="12759200000t" end="12795420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">现在也变成了昴君的愉快小伙伴</p>
<p begin="12799870000t" end="12831330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">这个转变之快还真是吓到我了呢</p>
<p begin="12842040000t" end="12861910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">你这家伙的言语还真轻挑啊</p>
<p begin="12862160000t" end="12871270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">罗兹瓦尔</p>
<p begin="12880020000t" end="12894240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">轻挑…吗</p>
<p begin="12901660000t" end="12922810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">连至今为止10年的岁月</p>
<p begin="12923050000t" end="12943110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">所持续坚持下来的想法</p>
<p begin="12943350000t" end="12963760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">都能这样轻易放手的你嘴里</p>
<p begin="12964000000t" end="12978070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430">说出轻挑这种话</p>
<p begin="12978320000t" end="12996600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431">还真是难笑的笑话呢</p>
<p begin="13006680000t" end="13029500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432">愿望是不会消失的</p>
<p begin="13029740000t" end="13066670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433">你如果爱着母亲和家人的话</p>
<p begin="13066910000t" end="13085170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434">真心爱着他们的话</p>
<p begin="13085410000t" end="13112200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435">会那么轻易地就改变吗</p>
<p begin="13118290000t" end="13137320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436">还是说你其实</p>
<p begin="13137560000t" end="13162440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437">并不爱自己的母亲还有家人呢</p>
<p begin="13167990000t" end="13199010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438">爪牙被折断这种程度就扭曲的思念</p>
<p begin="13199250000t" end="13222980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439">这就是你的10年是吗</p>
<p begin="13227280000t" end="13246500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440">不要误会了</p>
<p begin="13253850000t" end="13267060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441">误会</p>
<p begin="13270730000t" end="13298720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442">本大爷可不是因为打输了</p>
<p begin="13298960000t" end="13319840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443">才跟着大将的</p>
<p begin="13327020000t" end="13361140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444">本大爷这10年都被过去捆绑着</p>
<p begin="13361380000t" end="13376560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445">过了10年…</p>
<p begin="13376800000t" end="13400540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle446">终于面对了那过往回忆</p>
<p begin="13400780000t" end="13421480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle447">面对过去…</p>
<p begin="13421720000t" end="13433490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle448">你…</p>
<p begin="13433730000t" end="13453580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle449">本大爷可没打算说在那里见到了什么</p>
<p begin="13453830000t" end="13487110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle450">以及为什么会跟着大将</p>
<p begin="13493270000t" end="13507000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle451">不过</p>
<p begin="13507250000t" end="13515420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle452">就只跟你说一个</p>
<p begin="13515670000t" end="13542440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle453">让本大爷不选择你而选择跟着大将</p>
<p begin="13542770000t" end="13565690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle454">的决定性理由</p>
<p begin="13583030000t" end="13617620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle455">比起被说<br />"你好弱啊, 给我保持那就好"</p>
<p begin="13623310000t" end="13661200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle456">会跟随被说<br />"因为你很强所以你是必要的"的人</p>
<p begin="13661450000t" end="13677680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle457">不是很理所当然的吗</p>
<p begin="13703840000t" end="13714810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle458">怎样啦</p>
<p begin="13715050000t" end="13732170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle459">不, 没什么</p>
<p begin="13737480000t" end="13751170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle460">真靠得住呢</p>
<p begin="13776670000t" end="13796210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle461">加菲尔面对了过去</p>
<p begin="13800660000t" end="13817850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle462">就算最后他选择站在这里</p>
<p begin="13823470000t" end="13865300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle463">那也不表示这10年中<br />他对家人的思念就有所淡化了</p>
<p begin="13870390000t" end="13893800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle464">那份思念的强度应该没有丝毫改变</p>
<p begin="13900440000t" end="13912720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle465">只是思念不变的同时</p>
<p begin="13912960000t" end="13928470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle466">他有所改变了而已</p>
<p begin="13942930000t" end="13960900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle467">你也是一样的</p>
<p begin="13961140000t" end="13998830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle468">只要做法能够方向一致的话</p>
<p begin="13999070000t" end="14013000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle469">我们就可以一起努力</p>
<p begin="14018620000t" end="14035280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle470">现在还来得及收手</p>
<p begin="14062700000t" end="14076910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle471">优势仍然</p>
<p begin="14077150000t" end="14090650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle472">还在我这边</p>
<p begin="14090890000t" end="14103840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle473">你说什么</p>
<p begin="14104080000t" end="14118060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle474">打赌的条件当中</p>
<p begin="14118300000t" end="14142950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle475">你束缚了自己所拥有的最强武器</p>
<p begin="14143190000t" end="14159200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle476">变成了一个普通人</p>
<p begin="14163180000t" end="14193570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle477">就你一个普通人能做到什么</p>
<p begin="14193810000t" end="14212670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle478">什么都做不到</p>
<p begin="14212910000t" end="14228180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle479">怎么可能做得了什么</p>
<p begin="14228420000t" end="14254110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle480">比一般人还不如的你能做什么</p>
<p begin="14254360000t" end="14272190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle481">这里可是铭刻着多少岁月的思念</p>
<p begin="14272430000t" end="14293860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle482">不管是谁都无法侵入的圣域</p>
<p begin="14294100000t" end="14316290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle483">不管是谁都无法改变这件事</p>
<p begin="14316530000t" end="14332630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle484">我的400年</p>
<p begin="14332880000t" end="14357250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle485">怎么可能让你一个普通人</p>
<p begin="14357500000t" end="14374080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle486">就这样轻易颠覆</p>
<p begin="14382910000t" end="14404920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle487">因为思念是不会变化的东西吗</p>
<p begin="14405160000t" end="14415160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle488">就是这样</p>
<p begin="14415390000t" end="14430430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle489">正是因为长时间</p>
<p begin="14430670000t" end="14451590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle490">一直持续相信着</p>
<p begin="14451830000t" end="14466880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle491">是啊, 正是如此</p>
<p begin="14467120000t" end="14485110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle492">那么为什么你只在意</p>
<p begin="14485350000t" end="14511290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle493">自己所想的事物有多弱小呢</p>
<p begin="14511530000t" end="14533650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle494">你明明知道只要一个人一直持续思念着</p>
<p begin="14533900000t" end="14555680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle495">就是多么强大的念头</p>
<p begin="14555930000t" end="14586010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle496">那为什么你只在意<br />那些弱小的部分呢</p>
<p begin="14586250000t" end="14620500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle497">因为我是如此相信的</p>
<p begin="14627060000t" end="14651760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle498">就像你相信着某个人的强大</p>
<p begin="14652000000t" end="14662570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle499">而有所期待一样</p>
<p begin="14662810000t" end="14699830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle500">我则是相信着人会维持弱小</p>
<p begin="14700070000t" end="14712630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle501">弱小又脆弱</p>
<p begin="14712870000t" end="14738170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle502">除了唯一重要的事物以外</p>
<p begin="14738410000t" end="14756820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle503">其余的都无法顺心如意的</p>
<p begin="14757060000t" end="14772180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle504">渺小的存在而已</p>
<p begin="14772420000t" end="14791680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle505">我就是如此相信的</p>
<p begin="14791920000t" end="14804870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle506">400年</p>
<p begin="14805110000t" end="14829490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle507">我只持续想着一位女性</p>
<p begin="14834190000t" end="14883790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle508">持续着无法接触她的时光<br />甚至比我们共同生活过的时间更加漫长</p>
<p begin="14884040000t" end="14897560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle509">但那身姿仍烙印在我心中</p>
<p begin="14897800000t" end="14906590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle510">久久不能离去</p>
<p begin="14910960000t" end="14942610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle511">让我的灵魂煎熬不已</p>
<p begin="14960070000t" end="14974020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle512">从那别离之日起</p>
<p begin="14974270000t" end="14996760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle513">我的心就已经完全粉碎了</p>
<p begin="14997000000t" end="15021860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle514">我什么都没有改变</p>
<p begin="15045690000t" end="15062930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle515">我再说一次</p>
<p begin="15067230000t" end="15091690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle516">现在依然是我保有优势</p>
<p begin="15096150000t" end="15116690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle517">虽然和书中所记载的有些差异</p>
<p begin="15116930000t" end="15128730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle518">但那又如何</p>
<p begin="15137010000t" end="15151490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle519">对我和你来说</p>
<p begin="15151730000t" end="15180110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle520">只要重要的其中一人还在</p>
<p begin="15180350000t" end="15196470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle521">就永远不会分出胜负</p>
<p begin="15203110000t" end="15224850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle522">别小看爱蜜莉雅了</p>
<p begin="15225090000t" end="15234910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle523">那孩子已经</p>
<p begin="15235150000t" end="15255130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle524">不会如你所愿地行动了</p>
<p begin="15255380000t" end="15273370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle525">她将会跨越所有的困难</p>
<p begin="15273620000t" end="15292530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle526">她怎么可能跨越得了</p>
<p begin="15292770000t" end="15304400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle527">失去了依靠</p>
<p begin="15304640000t" end="15329810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle528">被自己内心的后悔给压垮</p>
<p begin="15330050000t" end="15360140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle529">抱着"能有所改变"<br />这样巨大的希望而后悔</p>
<p begin="15360380000t" end="15381950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle530">放声大哭依靠你</p>
<p begin="15382190000t" end="15395280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle531">还真是相配啊</p>
<p begin="15395520000t" end="15424560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle532">怎么可能会有女孩<br />适合哭泣着的表情</p>
<p begin="15424800000t" end="15448240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle533">会像那样鳖脚地哭泣的女孩</p>
<p begin="15448490000t" end="15469580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle534">我可从来没有看过</p>
<p begin="15469820000t" end="15493040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle535">受伤, 被轻视</p>
<p begin="15493290000t" end="15516900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle536">那就是半妖精的宿命</p>
<p begin="15522370000t" end="15542770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle537">和"嫉妒的魔女"同样的出身</p>
<p begin="15543010000t" end="15564560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle538">是从出生开始就必须背负的诅咒</p>
<p begin="15564800000t" end="15601070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle539">会被蔑视为"魔女"也只是必然</p>
<p begin="15608420000t" end="15621810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle540">别开玩笑了</p>
<p begin="15622050000t" end="15639150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle541">那孩子哪里是魔女</p>
<p begin="15639390000t" end="15675290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle542">是你们擅自把那孩子当作魔女的吧</p>
<p begin="15675530000t" end="15707360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle543">有谁为那孩子说过或做过些什么吗</p>
<p begin="15707600000t" end="15718000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle544">痛苦的时候</p>
<p begin="15718250000t" end="15725640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle545">悲伤的时候</p>
<p begin="15725880000t" end="15738470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle546">就算哭泣也没关系</p>
<p begin="15741200000t" end="15761010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle547">如果无法自己擦干眼泪的话</p>
<p begin="15761250000t" end="15782410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle548">只要身旁有人能帮自己擦干就好了</p>
<p begin="15782650000t" end="15814040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle549">那其中当然也包含了你</p>
<p begin="15814280000t" end="15840140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle550">但你有为她说过或做过些什么吗</p>
<p begin="15847880000t" end="15857910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle551">如果谁都不做的话</p>
<p begin="15858150000t" end="15873310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle552">就由我来吧</p>
<p begin="15877310000t" end="15905130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle553">思念也好…诅咒也罢</p>
<p begin="15905370000t" end="15936090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle554">对相信一切都没有改变余地的你</p>
<p begin="15936330000t" end="15961210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle555">我们一定会彻底击倒</p>
<p begin="15966440000t" end="15988590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle556">我的名字是菜月昴</p>
<p begin="15988830000t" end="16008280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle557">是银色的半妖精</p>
<p begin="16008520000t" end="16028080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle558">爱蜜莉雅的骑士</p>
<p begin="16068550000t" end="16083510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle559">爱蜜莉雅就要来了</p>
<p begin="16083750000t" end="16095240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle560">罗兹瓦尔</p>
<p begin="16095480000t" end="16126920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle561">你擅自认定弱小的女孩</p>
<p begin="16127160000t" end="16161260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle562">会来将你最后的希望给彻底斩断</p>
<p begin="16174140000t" end="16200590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle563">果然如我意料的一样</p>
<p begin="16200830000t" end="16213830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle564">菜月昴</p>
<p begin="16214070000t" end="16225860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle565">什么</p>
<p begin="16229840000t" end="16253400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle566">你和我果然很相像</p>
<p begin="16264420000t" end="16276260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle567">在对自己思念的人</p>
<p begin="16276500000t" end="16304390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle568">强加上自己的理想这点…呢</p>
<p begin="16309470000t" end="16324840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle569">只是你认定的是弱小</p>
<p begin="16329370000t" end="16349360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle570">而我认定的是强大吗</p>
<p begin="16358190000t" end="16372450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle571">说我们很相像这部分</p>
<p begin="16372700000t" end="16397970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle572">只有这一点我就承认吧</p>
<p begin="16423130000t" end="16433300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle573">走啰</p>
<p begin="16485740000t" end="16507490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle574">你这个大笨蛋<br />(圣域起始之初及崩坏的开始)</p>
<p begin="16618160000t" end="16626880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle575">好</p>
<p begin="16630940000t" end="16641490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle576">没问题了</p>
<p begin="16749060000t" end="16763010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle577">欢迎您回来</p>
<p begin="16763250000t" end="16773930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle578">爱蜜莉雅大人</p>
</div>
